uint16_t MmwDemo_RFParserOutParams_t::numDopplerBins

uint16_t MmwDemo_RFParserOutParams_t::numDopplerChirps

Number of chirps for Doppler computation purposes. For example, in TDM/BPM-MIMO scheme, this is the physical chirps in a frame per transmit antenna i.e numDopplerChirps = numChirpsPerFrame / numTxAntennas.

uint16_t MmwDemo_RFParserOutParams_t::numRangeBins

Number of range FFT bins, this is at a minimum the next power of 2 of numAdcSamples. If range zoom is supported, this can be bigger than the minimum.
